00:00:19.699 --> 00:00:23.280
Hey, whatever hatched from that egg isn't what our team came here to kill.

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:24.920
Focus on the Queen, Ant.

00:00:25.379 --> 00:00:29.699
I say that, but it's unsettling. They keep on evolving.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Man, if there's an ant out there that was born from an egg of this size...

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Damn bugs. These shitheads mean war.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.500
Got munched pretty good.

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:43.399
You want me to patch you up there, buddy?

00:00:43.399 --> 00:00:44.799
Gotta pay the price, though.

00:00:45.299 --> 00:00:48.000
Quit being a screwy brat. Just do it.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:50.000
Okay, but there's something that I want.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:52.500
And no, it isn't money this time around. I...

00:00:53.799 --> 00:00:55.799
More incoming. Fine.

00:00:55.799 --> 00:00:58.200
Alright, Chimizu. Whatever you want.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:13.340
Chimizu's

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:25.879
This school isы

