00:01:29.019 --> 00:01:29.680
Sorry, can we stop here?

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:30.000
Yeah. How about next time? Please.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:34.000
Bad face, bad situation

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:39.000
Bad love, bad feeling

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:41.000
I can't get over it, no no

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:43.000
Kiss me

